# Release Checklist

- Ensure all channel operations are channel-scoped and tested with at least 2 sources.
- Verify no plaintext secret is written to logs, config exports, or UI.
- Verify install/uninstall scripts work on a clean BT panel environment.
- Verify API methods used by UI exist and return stable response formats.
- Document new endpoints and behavior changes in `README.md` (Chinese first).
- Keep design docs, development docs, and development trace logs updated.
- Confirm stage self-test report is recorded before commit/push.
- Use Chinese commit message and push after stage acceptance.
